<item>
            <title>[LU-13868] lower than  and greater than compare operator support for PCC rule</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13868</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;There are increasing requirements to add lower than/greater than compare operator for the PCC rules:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;File data that is larger than local disk capacity should not auto cache in PCC;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;A range of UID/GID/ProjID could be auto cached on PCC;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;The following rule expressions are supported:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
lctl pcc add /mnt/lustre /mnt/pcc -p &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;projid=\{100}&amp;amp;size&amp;gt;\{1M}&amp;amp;size&amp;lt;\{500G}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
lctl pcc add /mnt/lustre /mnt/pcc -p &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;projid&amp;gt;\{100}&amp;amp;projid&amp;lt;\{110}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
lctl pcc add /mnt/lustre /mnt/pcc -p &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;uid&amp;lt;\{1500}&amp;amp;uid&amp;gt;\{1000}&quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
